very nice flat. Good personnel space for spending time with family or friends.

Rahuls place is perfectly located if you want easy access to local shopping, restaurants, and a short distance to Darjeeling More where the Jeeps pick up tourists to take to Darjeeling and other locales in the adjacent mountain regions. If you’re interested in tea there are some historic auction houses right there, and while the main roads to trains stations and airport are close by, the apartment itself is in a gated complex a little out of the hustle and bustle.
We had a great experience staying at this place, host was responsive and all the amenities were covered well.
it was a nice and relaxing stay at Rahul's place. Will recommend for short and family trips
